## Agenda Setting Workflow

Build an effective meeting agenda:

- [ ] 1. Clarify purpose: Define the meeting objective ({{meeting_objective}})
- [ ] 2. Identify outcomes: What decisions or outputs are needed
- [ ] 3. Structure flow: Sequence topics from information sharing to decision-making
- [ ] 4. Time allocation: Assign realistic time blocks to each agenda item
- [ ] 5. Assign owners: Designate facilitators for each topic ({{facilitators}})
- [ ] 6. Pre-work: Identify what attendees need to prepare

## Inputs
- Meeting type: {{meeting_type}}
- Attendees: {{attendees}}
- Duration: {{duration}}
- Objective: {{meeting_objective}}
